    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──The morning of the third week.\nLast week's massage must have gone well—I'm starting to feel Nana's trust in me."
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(She's come two weeks in a row... Could this mean...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(No, it's too early to tell. But she definitely likes my treatments.)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(Maybe today... I can go a little further...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(But first, let me check last week's finances...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "triggerWeeklySettlement": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(…As I thought, the fixed costs are too high. At this rate, I'm running in the red, let alone paying off my debt...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(The door chime rang. Is that Nana?)"
    },
    {
      "character": "tatsu",
      "expression": "normal",
