    {
      "id": "tatsu_threat",
      "character": "tatsu",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "...I just came to check on you today. Next time, there won't be any mercy.",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "tatsu",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "If you can't pay next time, I'll have you sell your organs. You can live with just one kidney, right?",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(That's terrifying... But still, Tatsu's shoulders look so stiff. Supporting those heavy breasts...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "tatsu",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "See ya. Better be prepared for when I come next time.",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(The sound of the door closing... Hah... I got threatened again...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(But even Tatsu looks like she needs treatment... With those huge boobs, her shoulder pain must be terrible... Wait, what am I thinking?)"
